<br>
I don't care who gets to nuke for the most damage, best nuke ratio, or anything to do with nukes.  Mages are not nukers (My opinoin only, and opinions are like..., everyone's got one, and they all stink).  I don't care about the DS with druids either.  I have never heard of a situation where lack of 1 or 2 points on a group DS means raid wipe out, so, the DS issue for me is nothing.  <br>
<br>
What is the class defineing point of being a Mage?  Pets.  Thats it.  No matter what, without exception, we should have the best pets, and pet buffs in the game.  We don't now, (think of the Dire Charmed pets, or the buffs Beastlords get), but we should.  This is why Mages are Mages, pets.<br>
<br>
In sum:  I think the only way I will be Ok with the PoP spells is if we get the best pets, and it does not seem as if we are going to.   <br>
